# SEQUENCE 05 — THE PRINCE AND THE SHADOW

/* TRACE: FU-025 | SC-107 */

INT. CHITRAPATHI'S RECEIVING ROOM — LATE AFTERNOON #35#

CHITRAPATHI receives UDAYAKUMARAN without ceremony.

The room carries the evidence of an artistic household under strain: instruments kept in repair, account cords retied, a costume chest left unopened.

CHITRAPATHI
A house like ours survives because powerful people remember its value.

UDAYAKUMARAN
You asked for me because Manimekalai has forgotten mine.